The,SkyWise,Insight,API,allows,developers,to,access,historical,current,and,forecast,data,for,any,geographic,area,of,interest,Weather,information,is,updated,hourly,and,has,a,resolution,of,km,throughout,North,America,The,API,includes,endpoints,for,standard,weather,variables,as,well,as,some,industry,specific,metrics,such,as,Heating,Cooling,Degree,Days,Growing,Degree,Days,and,Evapotranspiration